jsp.jsp

Class status_jsp.QueueControlBlock

  • java.lang.Object
    • jsp.jsp.status_jsp.QueueControlBlock
  • Enclosing class:
    status_jsp

    class status_jsp.QueueControlBlock
extends Object
    The QueueControlBlock contains the static configuration and dynamic operational data/queues for queues specified in the statusConfig.xml The QueueControlBlocks are rebuilt when the statusConfig.xml is modified.

      • updateFileInfoCache

        void updateFileInfoCache()
        Update the FileInfo cache using a delta of the FileInfo cache contents and the file system contents. This saves time on not needing to reread .xml files for pdfPages on each invocation. The queueStatusLevel and queueStatusReason is also updated at this time.
